{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some checkboxes components."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a checkbox with only an indicator prefer instead "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"symbolKind":"struct","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","title":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents29OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminateV"},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/init(selection:label:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:isReadOnly:hasDivider:action:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/body"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","title":"Instance Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations","title":"Default Implementations"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitemindeterminate"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Layouts","anchor":"Layouts","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"inverse","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing checkbox indicator and a leading optional image"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Indicator states","anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"unselected","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"indeterminate"}]},{"type":"text","text":": mike a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you need a checkbox with only two states to manage use instead "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Particular cases","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"but this component must not be considered as disabled."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom checkbox trait.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Forbidden by design","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}]}]},{"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state checkbox","    @Published var selection: OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState = .indeterminate","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\")","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Bazinga!\", helper: \"Doll-Dagga Buzz-Buzz Ziggety-Zag\")","","    \/\/ A trailing checkbox with a label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection,","                                  label: \"We live in a fabled world\",","                                  helper: \"Of dreaming boys and wide-eyed girls\",","                                  isReversed: true,","                                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label and and icon but with the icon flipped vertically","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(isOn: $selection,","                                  labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                                  flipIcon: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to manage the RTL mode quite easily and switch your layouts (flip image, indicator in RTL leading i.e. in the right):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(isOn: $selection,","                                  labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                                  flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                                  isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Suggestions","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Suggestions"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"According to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/09d860-checkbox\/t\/14bf4bd854","type":"reference"},{"text":", the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Design documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/09d860-checkbox","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2.0.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Version"},{"style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}]}],"name":"Since"}]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate/body":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitemindeterminate\/body","title":"body","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{